<h2>1. Overview</h2>
<p>At <strong>Fominoo.com</strong>, we want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. We offer a <strong>30-day return window</strong> from the date of delivery for most items purchased on our website. This policy applies to all customers shipping to or from the United States and internationally.</p>
<p>Please read this Refund &amp; Return Policy carefully before making a purchase. By completing a purchase on Fominoo.com, you agree to the terms of this Policy.</p>

<h2>2. Return Eligibility</h2>
<h3>2.1 Items Eligible for Return</h3>
<p>To be eligible for a return, your item must meet <strong>all</strong> of the following conditions:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Returned within <strong>30 days</strong> of the delivery date</li>
  <li>Item is <strong>unworn, unwashed, and unused</strong></li>
  <li>All original <strong>tags and labels are attached</strong></li>
  <li>Item is in its <strong>original packaging</strong> (where applicable)</li>
  <li>Item was purchased directly from <strong>Fominoo.com</strong></li>
  <li>Item is <strong>not listed as a Final Sale item</strong></li>
</ul>

<h3>2.2 Non-Returnable Items</h3>
<p>The following items <strong>cannot be returned or exchanged</strong>:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Items marked as <strong>"Final Sale"</strong> or <strong>"Non-Returnable"</strong> at time of purchase</li>
  <li>Intimates, lingerie, swimwear (for hygiene reasons)</li>
  <li>Earrings and pierced jewelry (for hygiene reasons)</li>
  <li>Items that have been worn, washed, altered, or damaged after delivery</li>
  <li>Items with removed tags or original packaging</li>
  <li>Gift cards</li>
  <li>Personalized or custom-made items</li>
  <li>Hazardous materials or items that cannot be shipped by mail</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. How to Initiate a Return</h2>
<p>To start your return, follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Submit a Return Request:</strong> Email us at <a href="mailto:returns@fominoo.com">returns@fominoo.com</a> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact">Returns Portal</a> within 30 days of delivery. Include your order number, the item(s) you wish to return, and the reason for return.</li>
  <li><strong>Receive Return Authorization:</strong> Our team will review your request and email you a <strong>Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA)</strong> number and return shipping label within 2–3 business days.</li>
  <li><strong>Package Your Item:</strong> Securely pack your item(s) with the RMA number clearly written on the outside of the package.</li>
  <li><strong>Ship Your Return:</strong> Drop off your package at any authorized carrier location within <strong>7 business days</strong> of receiving your RMA. Returns without an authorized RMA number will not be accepted.</li>
</ol>

<h2>4. Return Shipping Costs</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Return Reason</th><th>Who Pays Shipping</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Item received damaged or defective</td><td><strong>Fominoo</strong> (free return label provided)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Wrong item received</td><td><strong>Fominoo</strong> (free return label provided)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Change of mind / fit issue</td><td><strong>Customer</strong> (shipping cost deducted from refund)</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Size exchange</td><td><strong>Customer</strong> for original return; free shipping on exchange order</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>5. Refund Processing</h2>
<p>Once your return is received and inspected:</p>
<ul>
  <li>We will notify you by email of the status of your refund within <strong>2–3 business days</strong> of receiving the item.</li>
  <li>If approved, your refund will be processed to your <strong>original payment method</strong> within <strong>5–10 business days</strong>.</li>
  <li>For credit/debit card refunds, additional time may be required depending on your card issuer's processing time.</li>
</ul>

<h3>5.1 Refund Options</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Original Payment Method Refund:</strong> Full purchase price minus return shipping cost (if applicable).</li>
  <li><strong>Store Credit:</strong> If you prefer store credit, we will issue a Fominoo gift card for the <strong>full purchase price</strong> with no deductions. Store credit never expires.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Damaged, Defective, or Incorrect Items</h2>
<p>If you receive an item that is damaged, defective, or not what you ordered, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@fominoo.com">support@fominoo.com</a> within <strong>48 hours of delivery</strong>. Include:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your order number</li>
  <li>Clear photos of the damaged or incorrect item</li>
  <li>A description of the issue</li>
</ul>
<p>We will provide a free return label and either replacement, exchange, or full refund at no cost to you.</p>

<h2>7. Exchanges</h2>
<p>We offer exchanges for <strong>different sizes or colors</strong> of the same item, subject to availability.</p>
<ul>
  <li>To request an exchange, follow the same return initiation process and specify your desired replacement item.</li>
  <li>Exchanges are processed after the original item is received and inspected.</li>
  <li>If the desired item is out of stock at the time of processing, we will issue a full refund or store credit.</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Late or Missing Refunds</h2>
<p>If you haven't received your refund within the stated timeframe:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Check your bank account or card statement again.</li>
  <li>Contact your credit card company — it may take additional processing time.</li>
  <li>Contact your bank — there is often a processing period before a refund is posted.</li>
  <li>If you've done all of the above and still have not received your refund, contact us at <a href="mailto:returns@fominoo.com">returns@fominoo.com</a>.</li>
</ol>

<h2>9. Sale &amp; Promotional Items</h2>
<p>Items purchased at a full regular price can be returned for a full refund. Items purchased on <strong>sale or with a promotional discount</strong> may only be returned for <strong>store credit</strong> (not a cash refund), unless they are defective. Final Sale items are <strong>not returnable</strong>.</p>

<h2>10. International Returns</h2>
<p>International customers (outside the USA) are responsible for all return shipping costs and any applicable customs duties or import fees. Fominoo does not reimburse customs or import fees for returned international orders. Please mark return packages as "Returned Goods" on customs forms to avoid additional duties.</p>

<h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
<blockquote>
  <strong>Fominoo Returns Team</strong><br>
  Email: <a href="mailto:returns@fominoo.com">returns@fominoo.com</a><br>
  Hours: Monday – Friday, 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM EST<br>
  Response time: Within 1–2 business days
</blockquote>

</div>

